                "category": "interaction",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>A slithering pit is so clear it's difficult to spot. A successful @Check[perception|dc:30] check is required to notice a stationary slithering pit, and a creature must be @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.Search]{Searching} to attempt this check.</p>\n<p>A creature that walks into the pit's space might fall into any active Dimensional Pit.</p>"
