                },
                "category": "defensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>Ingesting an extradimensional space like that found in a @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Spacious Pouch (Type I)]{Spacious Pouch} deals @Damage[6d8[force]] damage to the slithering pit and its occupants. The slithering pit then immediately uses Out You Go.</p>"
