                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The slithering pit makes a single pseudopod Strike against each target within range it doesn't already have @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Grabbed]. These attacks count toward the slithering pit's multiple attack penalty, but the penalty doesn't increase until after all of these attacks.</p>"
                },
